                with the proper structure, you can import it into LFS:
              </p>
              
              <div class="guide-code-block">
                <pre><code># Your COLMAP dataset should have this structure:
dataset/
├── images/              # Your input photos
│   ├── IMG_0001.jpg
│   ├── IMG_0002.jpg
│   └── ...
└── sparse/             # COLMAP output (0/ folder)
    └── 0/
        ├── cameras.bin     # or cameras.txt
        ├── images.bin      # or images.txt
        └── points3D.bin    # or points3D.txt</code></pre>
                <button class="guide-code-block__copy" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard">
