                the data in other applications. Here's what COLMAP produces and what each file contains.
              </p>

              <h3>Directory Structure</h3>
              <p>
                After running COLMAP's sparse reconstruction, you'll have this folder structure:
              </p>

              <div class="guide-file-tree">
                <div class="guide-file-tree__root">
                  <span class="guide-file-tree__icon">📁</span>
                  <span class="guide-file-tree__name">dataset/</span>
